MatchedObjectDescriptor.QualificationSummary:
Your resume must demonstrate at least one year of specialized experience at or equivalent to the GG/GS/09 grade level or pay band in the Federal service or equivalent experience in the private or public sector. Specialized experience must demonstrate the following: 1) Performing analytical and administrative work in supporting members involved in a variety of professional and administrative functions;
2) Drafting correspondence relating to administrative matters, and/or acts as a liaison in handling communication with persons and/or groups within and outside of the department;
3) Managing, arranging, and facilitating various conferences, meetings, committees as necessary in support of the department;
4) Scheduling events; notifying participants, arranging for space, travel accommodations, and ensuring all necessary arrangements/materials are prepared;
5) Planning, coordinating, managing, and conducting day-to-day administrative work for senior leadership. Additional qualification information can be found from the following Office of Personnel Management website: https://www.opm.gov/policy-data-oversight/classification-qualifications/general-schedule-qualification-standards/#url=List-by-Occupational-Series
